          "slidetitle": "What to Remember",
          "subtitle": "Essential points to carry forward always",
          "slidecontent": "• AI tools can miss dangerous drug combinations, so never rely on them as your only check\n• Always verify AI advice against a trusted clinical source or pharmacist\n• Patient context matters (allergies, age, kidney function) and AI may not have the full picture\n• When in doubt, escalate\n• Document any concerns about AI-generated interaction advice in the patient record\n• As a next step, practise running a familiar medication through an AI tool and then cross-checking the result manually"
